msgid ""
"For an example of editing a content item that is a bit different than adding"
" in the first place, we can examine editing an image. Editing an Image can "
"be done by navigating to an individual image and clicking the *Edit* tab. "
"Clicking the *Edit* tab for the image, you will see the following *Edit "
"Image* panel:"
