msgid ""
"Here, an image called \"Eastern Tiger Swallowtail Butterfly\" is being "
"edited.Â You can change the title and description, as usual, in which case "
"you would usually keep the setting to \"Keep existing image.\"Â You can also"
" change the image itself by checking the \"Replace with new image\" choice. "
"Or, clicking the \"Delete current image\" choice will simply delete the "
"image entirely."
